# Video Lectures Configuration
VIDEO_LECTURES_UPLOAD_PATH=/app/uploads
VIDEO_LECTURES_PROCESSED_PATH=/app/processed
VIDEO_LECTURES_THUMBNAIL_PATH=/app/thumbnails
